NK015(ba)023:0: kahdama pa rin po che'i bka' srol phur pa bka' ma lha nag gi rgyun khyer bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)023:1: na mo gu ru sh+r+ai badz+ra ku ma ra ya /
NK015(ba)023:5: thugs phrin las kyi dal gsum gyi /
NK015(ba)023:6: dang po la spyi don gsum /
NK015(ba)023:10: dang po la gnyis las mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK015(ba)023:12: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis brlabs so //
NK015(ba)023:15: skad cig gis rdo rje gzhon nu zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus dang sku mdog mthing ka /
NK015(ba)023:16: phyag drug gi dang po nas rim gyis phur pa dkar dmar mthing gsum dril ba /
NK015(ba)023:17: dpal dang dur khrod kyi chas rdzogs par gyur pa
NK015(ba)023:18: la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams 'dus shing thim par
NK015(ba)023:20: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK015(ba)023:21: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa /
NK015(ba)023:22: stobs chen khro bo chen po bcus //
NK015(ba)023:23: glad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK015(ba)023:24: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK015(ba)023:25: nga yi bka' la 'da' ma byed //
NK015(ba)023:26: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra bi dza ya ni
NK015(ba)023:27: la dan+da ya m+aan+ta ka +aar+ya a tsa la h+ya
NK015(ba)023:28: gri wa a pa ra tsit+ta a mri ta kun+da
NK015(ba)023:29: li tree lo kya bi dza ya ma h+aa ba
NK015(ba)023:30: la gardza ha na da ha pa tsa b+han+d+ha hu
NK015(ba)023:31: lu tish+tha tshin+d+ha b+hin+d+ha s+pho ta ya h'u phatah khro
NK015(ba)023:32: bo mthing nag phur bu bsnams pa bcus /
NK015(ba)023:33: bgegs kun phyogs skyongs bcur bstim phur bus btab /
NK015(ba)023:34: phur bu'i dab las me 'bar phyogs skyongs 'bar /
NK015(ba)023:35: ye shes ting 'dzin rnam rtog me 'bar srungs /
NK015(ba)023:37: badz+ra sa ma dzas bshags yul sad nas /
NK015(ba)023:41: ye nas gnyis med dang yig brgya bzla /
NK015(ba)023:42: tshogs zhing rnams kyis tshangs pa stsal nas rang la thim par bsam /
NK015(ba)023:43: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis /
NK015(ba)023:45: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK015(ba)023:46: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yi //
NK015(ba)023:47: ram yam kham gi me rlung chus //
NK015(ba)023:48: snod bcud dngos 'dzin dbyings su sbyangs //
NK015(ba)023:49: ci yang mi dmigs stong pa nyid //
NK015(ba)023:51: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK015(ba)023:52: rang rig zung 'jug h'u du gsal //
NK015(ba)023:53: e sogs las byung 'byung lnga'i dal //
NK015(ba)023:54: srog gi go ru shar ba dang //
NK015(ba)023:55: b+h+r+aum las khro bo'i gzhal yas khang //
NK015(ba)023:56: rgyan dang bkod pa rab rdzogs nang //
NK015(ba)023:57: e khram nyer gcig khyabs dang bcas //
NK015(ba)023:58: dbus su ru tra lha chen po //
NK015(ba)023:59: pho mo bzhi bsnol pad zla nyi //
NK015(ba)023:60: phyogs bcur e steng nyi ma la //
NK015(ba)023:61: phyogs skyongs pho mo byi ching mnan //
NK015(ba)023:62: g.yas g.yon bam ro rkyang pa dang //
NK015(ba)023:63: khyams la phyogs rer gsum gsum gyi //
NK015(ba)023:64: ro ni mgo med bcu gnyis gdan //
NK015(ba)023:65: rgyu yi h'u mthing gdan steng bab //
NK015(ba)023:66: rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa //
NK015(ba)023:67: lte bar h'u mthing mtshan pa las //
NK015(ba)023:68: spro bsdus don gnyis byas shing 'dus //
NK015(ba)023:69: snying gi go ru bsgom par bya //
NK015(ba)023:70: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK015(ba)023:71: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK015(ba)023:72: phung po rdo rje gtams byas nas //
NK015(ba)023:73: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK015(ba)023:74: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK015(ba)023:75: zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa //
NK015(ba)023:76: dkar dmar mthing ba'i zhal gsum la //
NK015(ba)023:77: g.yas gnyis rtse dgu lce lnga dang //
NK015(ba)023:78: g.yon gnyis kha t+w+aam me dpung bsnams //
NK015(ba)023:79: mtha' gnyis ri rab phur pa dril //
NK015(ba)023:80: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dbu la rdzogs //
NK015(ba)023:81: dur khrod dpal gyi chas kun rdzogs //
NK015(ba)023:82: rgyab zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum stabs //
NK015(ba)023:83: mdun zhabs g.yas bskum g.yon brkyang 'gyings //
NK015(ba)023:85: thod khrag bsnams te gnyis med sbyor //
NK015(ba)023:86: yab gsang nyi steng rdo rje h'u /
NK015(ba)023:88: phyi rtser phata la nang rtser //
NK015(ba)023:89: yum mkha' 'dab brgyad dmar po amh de dang thugs ka'i h'u yig las /
NK015(ba)023:92: zhal nas dbyibs brgyud mkha' ru bab //
NK015(ba)023:93: h'u mthing zung re phyogs bcur bab //
NK015(ba)023:94: khro bo phur pa dril ba la //
NK015(ba)023:96: g.yas g.yon khra phyag gnyis re te //
NK015(ba)023:97: mgo brnyan dang mtshungs sems can dang //
NK015(ba)023:98: g.yon pas phur dril chu srin zungs //
NK015(ba)023:99: stod g.yog kha nas phyag don pa /
NK015(ba)023:100: kun kyang mthing nag khro bo'i chas //
NK015(ba)023:101: me ri 'bar ba'i klong du brjid //
NK015(ba)023:102: sras mchog la ni e dkyil gyi //
NK015(ba)023:103: ngos gsum h'u yig bdun re spros //
NK015(ba)023:104: sku stod khro bo phur pa dril //
NK015(ba)023:105: sku smad gnam lcags phur bu'i dbal //
NK015(ba)023:106: skra bardzesa rgyan med rngam pa gsal //
NK015(ba)023:107: phyogs bzhi'i stod du shwa na bzhi //
NK015(ba)023:108: smad du bdag nyid ma bzhi gsal //
NK015(ba)023:109: sgo thad bswe mo bzhi gnas shing //
NK015(ba)023:110: rdo rwa'i nang du 'byung po ni //
NK015(ba)023:111: nyi shu rtsa gcig gnas par gyur //
NK015(ba)023:112: gnyis pa ye shes drang bstim ni /
NK015(ba)023:114: ye shes phur bu bsgrub pa dang //
NK015(ba)023:115: srid pa rdo rje grub pa'i phyir //
NK015(ba)023:116: lha tshogs 'khor bcas gshegs nas kyang //
NK015(ba)023:117: rmad byung rtags mtshan dngos grub stsol //
NK015(ba)023:118: zhes gsol ba btab pas bskyed pa dang 'dar ba'i ye shes la byon nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK015(ba)023:120: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK015(ba)023:121: srid pa'i rdo rje grub mdzod cig /
NK015(ba)023:122: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK015(ba)023:123: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK015(ba)023:125: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK015(ba)023:126: ngang nyid rdo rje chos dbyings la /
NK015(ba)023:128: / 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa //
NK015(ba)023:129: sku gsung thugs su bdag bskyed cig /
NK015(ba)023:130: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK015(ba)023:131: byams dang snying rje gang 'dul ba //
NK015(ba)023:132: yon tan phrin las rdzogs mdzad nas //
NK015(ba)023:133: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag stsol cig /
NK015(ba)023:134: ces sku gsung thugs yon phrin las lnga'i dbang dang
NK015(ba)023:135: byin rlabs thams cad la mnga' brnyes nas lha tshogs
NK015(ba)023:136: rnams bdag nyid la bstim mo //
NK015(ba)023:139: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK015(ba)023:140: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro /
NK015(ba)023:142: / 'dod pa'i yon tan mang pos rab brgyan te //
NK015(ba)023:143: thugs dam bzhin du ci bder bzhes nas kyang //
NK015(ba)023:144: bdag la dngos grub ma lus stsal du gsol //
NK015(ba)023:145: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata tip+ta tsakra i dam /
NK015(ba)023:150: ru pa shab+ta gan+d+he ra sa spar+she p+au dza ho /
NK015(ba)023:153: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)023:154: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)023:155: ma h+aa rak+ta la kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)023:156: ma h+aa b+ha limta la kh+aa hi /
NK015(ba)023:158: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i sogs kyis bstod /
NK015(ba)023:160: bdag rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil
NK015(ba)023:161: 'khor gyi steng du ye shes sems dpa' rang 'dra
NK015(ba)023:162: ba / de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rdo
NK015(ba)023:163: rje nag po rtse dgu pa yar bzhengs pa de'i
NK015(ba)023:164: lte ba khang seng stong par nyi ma'i steng du
NK015(ba)023:165: h+aum mthing nag gi mthar bskor du /
NK015(ba)023:166: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata ces pa'i 'bru dgu pas g.yas su 'khor bar bsgom la /
NK015(ba)023:168: sngags kyi sgra las 'od zer byung bas phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK015(ba)023:169: sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK015(ba)023:170: sgrib pa sbyangs slar sems can thams cad rdo rje
NK015(ba)023:172: yang 'od zer khro bo 'chol ba'i tshogs kyis chos
NK015(ba)023:173: kyi dbyings mtha' klas pa'i b+hud+d+ha'i zhing khams la thug
NK015(ba)023:174: gi bar du bkang nas bdud dang mu stegs thams
NK015(ba)023:175: cad tshar bcad / ma mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad dpa' bskyed /
NK015(ba)023:176: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni thugs mnyam pa nyid las bzhengs /
NK015(ba)023:177: nyan thos rang rgyal rnams ni 'gog pa las bslang /
NK015(ba)023:178: dgra bgegs thams cad tshar bcad /
NK015(ba)023:179: khams gsum gyi log rtog zil gyis non par bsam /
NK015(ba)023:181: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba b+hig+h+n+aana bam h'u
NK015(ba)023:182: phata dzahmh'u +aah zhes 'bru bcu bdun pa yang zla
NK015(ba)023:183: / bse mo bzhi'i spyi bor sa'i dkyil 'khor ser po gru bzhi'i steng du dkar po /
NK015(ba)023:184: shwa na bzhis mgrin par rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu gzhu dbyibs kyi steng du +aahdamara po /
NK015(ba)023:185: re ti bzhis snying kar me yi dkyil 'khor dmar
NK015(ba)023:186: po gru gsum steng du h'u mthing nag rnams kyi
NK015(ba)023:187: mthar rang sngags kyis bskor bar bsam /
NK015(ba)023:188: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK015(ba)023:193: mu ru mu ru ha bse mo bzhi /
NK015(ba)023:198: ma ma pa sham ku ru h'u /
NK015(ba)023:200: ma tam dz+ny+aa na ka ra i nan /
NK015(ba)023:203: ma ra dregs pa nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK015(ba)023:205: ni pra ma ta ye m+aa ra ye a ba
NK015(ba)023:206: ta ni ye dza ye bi dza ye a pa
NK015(ba)023:207: ra tsit+ta ye h'u h'u phata /
NK015(ba)023:208: 'od zer 'phros khams gsum dregs tshogs kun gyi srog snying dam can rnams la 'dus /
NK015(ba)023:209: dam can rnams kyi srog yig 'bru gsum po rang
NK015(ba)023:210: gi h'u gi zhabs kyu'i nang du 'dus par bsam
NK015(ba)023:212: phyi'i lha dang 'od zer thams cad tshur 'dus rang
NK015(ba)023:213: lus la zhugs bye'u phrug gi gshog pa la khra
NK015(ba)023:214: chag pa'i tshul du bltam par bsam la /
NK015(ba)023:215: dbyangs gsal yig brgya rten snying bzla /
NK015(ba)023:217: nyer bsdu slar ldang dang bsngo smon shis brjod dang bcas bya'o //
NK015(ba)023:218: gsum pa thugs phrin las kyi dal ni /
NK015(ba)023:219: rgyud ltar na gong gi ting 'dzin bstan pa dang /
NK015(ba)023:221: dbyings ma skyes stong pa la /
NK015(ba)023:222: ye shes ma 'gags pa lha'i rnal 'byor ma bskyed ye nas rdzogs pa'i tshul /
NK015(ba)023:223: sras dbyer med bde ba chen po rtsa ba byang
NK015(ba)023:224: chub kyi sems kyi cho 'phrul chen por bzla ba'o
NK015(ba)023:226: lha sngags sogs chos thams cad so sor ma 'dres par snang yang /
NK015(ba)023:227: mnyam nyid kyi ngang du rdzogs par rtogs pa gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba /
NK015(ba)023:228: de'i ngang la gnas pa la bsgom bya sgom byed med pa dmigs gtad med pa'i sgom pa /
NK015(ba)023:229: spyod lam yang de'i ngang la gnas pa bya ba rtsol med pa'i spyod pa /
NK015(ba)023:230: de las legs su spangs thob bral ba spangs thob
NK015(ba)023:231: med pa'i 'bras bu te de'i ngang du bzla ba'o
NK015(ba)023:232: // ngan sngags nye bar bsnyen pa byar 'dod na ni gzhung las gsal lo //
NK015(ba)023:233: thun mtshams tshogs kyi mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)023:234: tshogs rdzas sna tshogs spungs la /
NK015(ba)023:235: kro d+hi shwa ri sarba pra phyam bi shwa d+ha ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)023:236: stong pa'i ngang las tshogs snod b+hany+dza 'bar bar tshogs
NK015(ba)023:237: rdzas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'dod yon gyi rnam
NK015(ba)023:238: pa ma tshangs pa med pa so so'i lha mo'i
NK015(ba)023:239: rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas mchod pa'i sprin
NK015(ba)023:240: spro bar gyur / +aahmh'u ha ho h+r+aihmh'u /
NK015(ba)023:241: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK015(ba)023:242: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK015(ba)023:243: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK015(ba)023:244: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK015(ba)023:245: zhung chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK015(ba)023:246: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK015(ba)023:248: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK015(ba)023:249: ma h+aa g+ha na tsakra pu dza ho //
NK015(ba)023:250: zhes phud kyis mchod par bas tshim par rol /
NK015(ba)023:251: lhag ma la kha phru btab a ka ro sogs /
NK015(ba)023:252: ta ki ra tsa dzahlhaga mgron dgug /
NK015(ba)023:254: dkyil 'khor de yi phyi rim nas //
NK015(ba)023:255: dam can ma mo bcu gnyis dang //
NK015(ba)023:256: dregs pa nyi shu rtsa gcig sogs /
NK015(ba)023:258: / 'dir gshegs rgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK015(ba)023:259: dam nyams sdang ba'i dgra bo la //
NK015(ba)023:260: rtags phyung mtshan ma myur du ston //
NK015(ba)023:262: ya hi gats+tshasa rang gnas su gshegs /
NK015(ba)023:263: bla ma la gus snying rjer ldan //
NK015(ba)023:264: rdo rje gzhon nu grub nas kyang //
NK015(ba)023:265: skye shi med par 'gyur bar shog /
NK015(ba)023:266: zab mo'i don la sems pa dang //
NK015(ba)023:267: btsun mo'i khu ba mnyam zas can //
NK015(ba)023:268: skye zhing skye bar 'gyur bar shog /
NK015(ba)023:269: ces kahdama pa rin po che'i dgongs pa ltar btus te rgyun khyer du bkod pa'o //
NK015(ba)023:270: rje de'i brgyud 'dzin gyi ming tsam 'dzin pa bi
NK015(ba)023:271: dza'i ming gis bris pas rgyal bstan rgyas pa'i rgyur
